articles.description: Dr. Zach - who has sued former patients for claiming he botched their surgeries - posted a statement to his account but made no mention of the 33-year-old talent or the incident.
articles.content:
Late Wild 'N Out star Ms Jacky Oh's surgeon Dr. Zachary 'Dr. Zach' Okhah took to Instagram on Friday to break his silence two weeks after her death.
